articles.title: Rare hybrid solar eclipse will be visible Thursday - 25 News Now
articles.description: Australia as well as some locations in Southeast Asia will be able to see this rare occurrence on April 20.
articles.content:
(Gray News) Sky watchers can catch a glimpse of a rare hybrid solar eclipse Thursday, according to the National Aeronautics and Space Administration.
